snippet.title: PM Arrives In Changsari Venue: AASU Stages Protest, Burns Modi’s Effigy in Guwahati

localized.description:
As Prime Minister Narendra Modi arrived in Changsari at Kamrup from Arunachal Pradesh on February 9th, 2019, the activists of the All Assam Students’ Union (AASU) took out a protest rally in front of their head office Swahid Nyas Bhawan in Uzan Bazar area here and burnt the effigy of Modi and also waved black flags.
